data.title: Frederick County MD - Official Website
data.meta_description: Support options and resources for Frederick County employees.
data.text:
Frederick County employee pages are password protected and for the use of authorized Frederick County employees.

Office.com - For Microsoft web-based county resources such as: Microsoft Teams, SharePoint Online, Word Online, Excel Online, PowerPoint Online, OneDrive, and OneNote.

Remote Desktop - Provides access to internal County resources such as files and folders on the network (R, S, U Drives), Time Sheet, e-Mail, FCG Portal, Microsoft Office Suite (Word/Excel/Outlook) and departmental resources. This is a virtual computer like interface to many of the tools you use at work.
